      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 A solid, no-nonsense vehicle that delivers dependable everyday transportation! This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs reliably and handles your daily commute without fuss, making it a great choice for practical-minded buyers looking for value. It has some wear consistent with its age and use, but nothing that gets in the way of getting you where you need to go. If you're after honest, affordable transportation, this one deserves a look!",
