    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Mint condition beauty available now \u2014 and this one truly lives up to the label! Every detail of this vehicle has been carefully maintained, from the flawless, turn-heads exterior to the immaculate, like-new interior. The engine runs smoothly and everything works exactly as it should. If you've been searching for a vehicle that feels fresh off the lot without the new-car price tag, this is your opportunity \u2014 don't let it pass you by!",
      "price": 47500.0,
