      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable and dependable daily driver? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, making it a great practical choice for everyday commuting! You'll notice some cosmetic wear typical of a used vehicle, including minor exterior blemishes and some interior signs of use, but nothing that affects its road-worthiness. If you're after a no-fuss ride that gets the job done without a hefty price tag, this one's worth a look!",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront about what you're getting. The exterior shows extensive wear \u2014 expect multiple deep scratches, significant dents, faded and peeling paint, and visible rust in several areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn and stained upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and non-functional features throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it runs, but not reliably, and you should budget for meaningful repair costs. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs parts. We are pricing it accordingly to reflect its true state, and we encourage any serious buyer to inspect it thoroughly before purchasing.",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold as-is in poor condition, and the price reflects that honestly \u2014 please read carefully before reaching out. The car has significant mechanical issues and/or body/structural problems that go beyond normal wear and tear. It is not in reliable daily-driver shape and will likely require substantial repairs to bring it up to a roadworthy standard. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs it for parts. There are no major hidden surprises beyond what is described \u2014 what you see is what you get. If you have questions about specific issues, please ask before making an offer.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in poor condition, and we want any potential buyer to have a completely accurate picture before reaching out. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 there are multiple dents, scratches, and areas of rust that are clearly visible. The paint is faded and peeling in several spots, and the body panels show signs of previous minor collision damage that was not professionally repaired. Inside, the cabin is worn throughout: the upholstery is torn and stained, several trim pieces are cracked or missing, and the dashboard shows heavy sun damage. Mechanically, the car runs but requires attention \u2014 it has known issues including rough idling, a check engine light that has been on for some time, and the suspension feels loose. The tires have uneven wear and will need replacement soon. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with its current state. No warranties or guarantees are offered, and we strongly encourage an independent inspection prior to purchase.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    }
